---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Mezon — Serviços">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-50 md:text-5xl">Nossos Serviços</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-400">
        Soluções completas para transformar sua visão em realidade digital com governança e previsibilidade.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="flex flex-col rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/70 bg-slate-900/60 p-8 transition hover:border-sky-400/60">
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500/10 text-sky-300">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Desenvolvimento Web</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-400">
          Aplicações modernas e responsivas com as melhores tecnologias do mercado, alinhadas aos objetivos de negócio.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Single Page Apps e plataformas corporativas</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>E-commerce, marketplaces e portais</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Dashboards, BI e integrações</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="flex flex-col rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/70 bg-slate-900/60 p-8 transition hover:border-sky-400/60">
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500/10 text-sky-300">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Mobile & PWA</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-400">
          Experiências móveis nativas e híbridas, com foco em performance, usabilidade e publicação contínua.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Aplicativos iOS e Android</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Progressive Web Apps (PWA)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Integrações com APIs e serviços de nuvem</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="flex flex-col rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/70 bg-slate-900/60 p-8 transition hover:border-sky-400/60">
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500/10 text-sky-300">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Consultoria & Arquitetura</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-400">
          Análise técnica, planejamento e governança para garantir evolução sustentável dos seus produtos digitais.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Arquitetura de sistemas e cloud</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Revisões técnicas e auditorias</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>DevOps, SRE e observabilidade</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="flex flex-col rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/70 bg-slate-900/60 p-8 transition hover:border-sky-400/60">
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500/10 text-sky-300">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">APIs & Backend</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-400">
          APIs robustas, seguras e escaláveis para conectar sistemas, produtos e parceiros estratégicos.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>REST, GraphQL e microsserviços</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Integrações com sistemas legados</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Monitoração e observabilidade</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="flex flex-col rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/70 bg-slate-900/60 p-8 transition hover:border-sky-400/60">
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500/10 text-sky-300">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">UI/UX Design</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-400">
          Design centrado no usuário, com processos de descoberta, prototipagem e validação contínua.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Pesquisa, discovery e UX strategy</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Design systems e guias visuais</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Testes de usabilidade e métricas</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="flex flex-col rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/70 bg-slate-900/60 p-8 transition hover:border-sky-400/60">
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500/10 text-sky-300">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Manutenção & Suporte</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-400">
          Suporte contínuo, evolução e monitoramento para manter seus produtos confiáveis e atualizados.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Monitoramento 24/7 e alertas proativos</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Correções, hotfixes e hardening</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
            <span>Planejamento de roadmap contínuo</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-sky-500/40 bg-slate-900/60 p-12 text-center shadow-lg shadow-sky-950/30">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-50 md:text-4xl">Pronto para começar?</h3>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-300">
        Compartilhe seus objetivos e construa um plano com quem entende de produto, engenharia e resultados.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500 px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 shadow-lg shadow-sky-950/40 transition hover:bg-sky-400"
      >
        Solicitar orçamento
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
